Title: Dig a Hole
Plot: Crews and Reese investigate the murder of a Zen Master who was buried alive ten years ago.  Crews continues to investigate his own case.  He finds some proof that his partner's father Jack Reese could be involved.
GuestStars: Morann Peri, Chandler Parker, Jennifer Siebel, Fay Masterson, Jude Ciccolella, Roger Aaron Brown, Martin Grey, Merdith Gangrande, Erin Ross, Andrew Thacher, Brandon Inge, Matthew Leonard, Victor Rivers, Hillary Tu
